## ⚙️ Installation

### 1. Clone the repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/solution-42.git
cd solution-42
2. Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt
3. Run the application
streamlit run app.py
🧪 Usage
Enter your question
Provide your details
Click "Find the Answer"
Let the system compute
Receive your answer

Spoiler: It's always 42

💡 Key Learning Outcomes
Building interactive apps using Streamlit
Enhancing UX with animations and storytelling
Using randomness for dynamic outputs
Structuring engaging UI without complex backend

